    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Biemna spinomicroxea sp. n. (Holotype, MCNPOR 1887). A. Specimen preserved in alcohol (scale bar = 0.5 cm); B. Skeletal arrangement (scale bar = 300 µm); C. Oxea (scale bar = 100 µm); D. Detail of oxea extremities (scale bar = 10 µm); E. Spiny sigma (scale bar = 5 µm); F. Detail of sigma extremity (scale bar = 2 µm); G. Microxea I (scale bar = 20 µm); H. Detail of microxea I extremity (scale bar = 2 µm); I. Microxea II (scale bar = 20 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170498/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

